{"title_page": "Arata Watanabe", "text_new": "{{short description|Japanese footballer}}\n{{Infobox football biography\n| name = Arata Watanabe <br> \u6e21\u9089\u65b0\u592a\n| fullname = Arata Watanabe\n| birth_date = {{Birth date and age|1995|8|5}}\n| birth_place = [[Niigata, Niigata|Niigata]], Japan\n| height={{height|m=1.81}}\n| position = [[Forward (association football)|Forward]]\n| currentclub = [[Albirex Niigata]]\n| clubnumber = 11\n| youthyears1 = 2011\u20132013 | youthclubs1 = [[Albirex Niigata]] Youth\n| youthyears2 = 2014\u20132017 | youthclubs2 = [[Ryutsu Keizai University]]\n| years1 = 2018\u2013 | clubs1 = [[Albirex Niigata]] | caps1 = 35 | goals1 = 10\n| pcupdate = 3 January 2018\n}}\n\n{{nihongo|'''Arata Watanabe'''|\u6e21\u9089\u65b0\u592a|Watanabe Arata|born August 5, 1995}} is a Japanese [[Association football|football]] player for [[Albirex Niigata]].\n\n==Career==\nWhile attending [[Ryutsu Keizai University]], [[Albirex Niigata]] watched Watanabe and even signed him as a special designated player in the [[2017 J1 League|2017 season]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.albirex.co.jp/news/top_team/52758/|title=\u6d41\u901a\u7d4c\u6e08\u5927\u5b66 \u6e21\u9089 \u65b0\u592a\u9078\u624b\u3000\u300eJFA\u30fbJ\u30ea\u30fc\u30b0\u7279\u5225\u6307\u5b9a\u9078\u624b\u300f \u627f\u8a8d\u306e\u304a\u77e5\u3089\u305b|website=\u30a2\u30eb\u30d3\u30ec\u30c3\u30af\u30b9\u65b0\u6f5f \u516c\u5f0f\u30b5\u30a4\u30c8\uff5cALBIREX NIIGATA OFFICIAL WEBSITE|accessdate=27 August 2018}}</ref> In January 2018, Watanabe joined Albirex's top team and scored in four consecutive games during the [[2018 J2 League|2018 season]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.albirex.co.jp/news/top_team/52732/|title=\u6e21\u9089 \u65b0\u592a\u9078\u624b\uff08\u6d41\u901a\u7d4c\u6e08\u5927\u5b66\uff09\u6765\u5b63\u65b0\u52a0\u5165\u5185\u5b9a\u306e\u304a\u77e5\u3089\u305b|website=\u30a2\u30eb\u30d3\u30ec\u30c3\u30af\u30b9\u65b0\u6f5f \u516c\u5f0f\u30b5\u30a4\u30c8\uff5cALBIREX NIIGATA OFFICIAL WEBSITE|accessdate=27 August 2018}}</ref>\n\n==Club statistics==\n''Updated to end of 2018 season''.<ref>Nippon Sports Kikaku Publishing inc./\u65e5\u672c\u30b9\u30dd\u30fc\u30c4\u4f01\u753b\u51fa\u7248\u793e, [https://www.amazon.co.jp/J1-J3%E9%81%B8%E6%89%8B%E5%90%8D%E9%91%91%E3%83%8F%E3%83%B3%E3%83%87%E3%82%A3%E7%89%88-2018-NSK-MOOK/dp/4905411521 \"J1&J2&J3\u9078\u624b\u540d\u9451\u30cf\u30f3\u30c7\u30a3\u7248 2018 (NSK MOOK)\"], 7 February 2018, Japan, {{ISBN|978-4905411529}} (p. 161 out of 289)</ref>\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|-\n! colspan=3 | Club performance\n! colspan=2 | League\n! colspan=2 | Cup\n! colspan=2 | League Cup\n! colspan=2 | Total\n|-\n! Season\n! Club\n! League\n! Apps !! Goals\n! Apps !! Goals\n! Apps !! Goals\n! Apps !! Goals\n|-\n! colspan=3 |Japan\n! colspan=2 | League\n! colspan=2 | [[Emperor's Cup]]\n! colspan=2 | [[J. League Cup]]\n! colspan=2 | Total\n|-\n|[[2018 J2 League|2018]]||rowspan=\"1\"|[[Albirex Niigata]]||rowspan=\"1\"|[[J2 League]]||35||10||2||0||3||0||40||10\n|-\n!colspan=3|Total\n!35||10||2||0||3||0||40||10\n|}\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n*{{J.League player}}\n*[https://www.jleague.jp/club/niigata/player/detail/1503340/ Profile at J. League]\n*[http://www.albirex.co.jp/clubs/6221/top_player?club=10 Profile at Albirex Niigata]\n\n{{Albirex Niigata squad}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Watanabe, Arata}}\n[[Category:1995 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Association football people from Niigata Prefecture]]\n[[Category:Japanese footballers]]\n[[Category:J2 League players]]\n[[Category:Albirex Niigata players]]\n[[Category:Association football forwards]]\n\n\n{{Japan-footy-forward-1990s-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{short description|Japanese footballer}}\n{{Infobox football biography\n| name = Arata Watanabe <br> \u6e21\u9089\u65b0\u592a\n| fullname = Arata Watanabe\n| birth_date = {{Birth date and age|1995|8|5}}\n| birth_place = [[Niigata, Niigata|Niigata]], Japan\n| height={{height|m=1.81}}\n| position = [[Forward (association football)|Forward]]\n| currentclub = [[Albirex Niigata]]\n| clubnumber = 11\n| youthyears1 = 2011\u20132013 | youthclubs1 = [[Albirex Niigata]] Youth\n| youthyears2 = 2014\u20132017 | youthclubs2 = [[Ryutsu Keizai University]]\n| years1 = 2018\u2013 | clubs1 = [[Albirex Niigata]] | caps1 = 35 | goals1 = 10\n| pcupdate = 3 January 2018\n}}\n\n{{nihongo|'''Arata Watanabe'''|\u6e21\u9089\u65b0\u592a|Watanabe Arata|born August 5, 1995}} is a Japanese [[Association football|football]] player for [[Albirex Niigata]].\n\n==Career==\nWhile attending [[Ryutsu Keizai University]], [[Albirex Niigata]] watched Watanabe and even signed him as a special designated player in the [[2017 J1 League|2017 season]]. <ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.albirex.co.jp/news/top_team/52758/|title=\u6d41\u901a\u7d4c\u6e08\u5927\u5b66 \u6e21\u9089 \u65b0\u592a\u9078\u624b\u3000\u300eJFA\u30fbJ\u30ea\u30fc\u30b0\u7279\u5225\u6307\u5b9a\u9078\u624b\u300f \u627f\u8a8d\u306e\u304a\u77e5\u3089\u305b|website=\u30a2\u30eb\u30d3\u30ec\u30c3\u30af\u30b9\u65b0\u6f5f \u516c\u5f0f\u30b5\u30a4\u30c8\uff5cALBIREX NIIGATA OFFICIAL WEBSITE|accessdate=27 August 2018}}</ref> In January 2018, Watanabe joined Albirex's top team and scored in four consecutive games during the [[2018 J2 League|2018 season]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.albirex.co.jp/news/top_team/52732/|title=\u6e21\u9089 \u65b0\u592a\u9078\u624b\uff08\u6d41\u901a\u7d4c\u6e08\u5927\u5b66\uff09\u6765\u5b63\u65b0\u52a0\u5165\u5185\u5b9a\u306e\u304a\u77e5\u3089\u305b|website=\u30a2\u30eb\u30d3\u30ec\u30c3\u30af\u30b9\u65b0\u6f5f \u516c\u5f0f\u30b5\u30a4\u30c8\uff5cALBIREX NIIGATA OFFICIAL WEBSITE|accessdate=27 August 2018}}</ref>\n\n==Club statistics==\n''Updated to end of 2018 season''.<ref>Nippon Sports Kikaku Publishing inc./\u65e5\u672c\u30b9\u30dd\u30fc\u30c4\u4f01\u753b\u51fa\u7248\u793e, [https://www.amazon.co.jp/J1-J3%E9%81%B8%E6%89%8B%E5%90%8D%E9%91%91%E3%83%8F%E3%83%B3%E3%83%87%E3%82%A3%E7%89%88-2018-NSK-MOOK/dp/4905411521 \"J1&J2&J3\u9078\u624b\u540d\u9451\u30cf\u30f3\u30c7\u30a3\u7248 2018 (NSK MOOK)\"], 7 February 2018, Japan, {{ISBN|978-4905411529}} (p. 161 out of 289)</ref>\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|-\n! colspan=3 | Club performance\n! colspan=2 | League\n! colspan=2 | Cup\n! colspan=2 | League Cup\n! colspan=2 | Total\n|-\n! Season\n! Club\n! League\n! Apps !! Goals\n! Apps !! Goals\n! Apps !! Goals\n! Apps !! Goals\n|-\n! colspan=3 |Japan\n! colspan=2 | League\n! colspan=2 | [[Emperor's Cup]]\n! colspan=2 | [[J. League Cup]]\n! colspan=2 | Total\n|-\n|[[2018 J2 League|2018]]||rowspan=\"1\"|[[Albirex Niigata]]||rowspan=\"1\"|[[J2 League]]||35||10||2||0||3||0||40||10\n|-\n!colspan=3|Total\n!35||10||2||0||3||0||40||10\n|}\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n*{{J.League player}}\n*[https://www.jleague.jp/club/niigata/player/detail/1503340/ Profile at J. League]\n*[http://www.albirex.co.jp/clubs/6221/top_player?club=10 Profile at Albirex Niigata]\n\n{{Albirex Niigata squad}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Watanabe, Arata}}\n[[Category:1995 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Association football people from Niigata Prefecture]]\n[[Category:Japanese footballers]]\n[[Category:J2 League players]]\n[[Category:Albirex Niigata players]]\n[[Category:Association football forwards]]\n\n{{Japan-footy-forward-stub}}\n", "name_user": "Joeykai", "label": "safe", "comment": "clean up", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Arata_Watanabe"}
