{"title_page": "Alan Pinheiro", "text_new": "{{short description|Brazilian footballer}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=March 2020}}\n{{Infobox football biography\n| name           = Alan Pinheiro\n| fullname       = Alan Lopes Pinheiro\n| image                =\n| height               = {{height|m=1.80|precision=0}}\n| birth_date           = {{birth date and age|df=y|1992|5|13}}\n| birth_place          = [[Brumado]], [[Brazil]]\n| currentclub          = [[JEF United Chiba]]\n| clubnumber           = 21\n| position             = [[Forward (association football)|Forward]]\n| years1   = 2012\u20132015 | clubs1 = [[Esporte Clube Vit\u00f3ria|Vit\u00f3ria]] | caps1   = 21 | goals1   = 19\n| years2   = 2013      | clubs2 = \u2192 [[Cear\u00e1 Sporting Club|Cear\u00e1]] (loan) | caps2   = 1 | goals2   =1\n| years3   = 2013      | clubs3 = \u2192 [[Kawasaki Frontale]] (loan) | caps3   = 10 | goals3   = 0\n| years4   = 2014      | clubs4 = \u2192 [[Agremia\u00e7\u00e3o Sportiva Arapiraquense|ASA]] (loan) | caps4   = 6 | goals4   = 3\n| years5   = 2015      | clubs5 = \u2192 [[Tokyo Verdy]] (loan) | caps5 = 31 | goals5 = 3\n| years6   = 2016\u20132018 | clubs6 = [[Tokyo Verdy]] | caps6 = 91 | goals6 = 26\n| years7   = 2019\u2013     | clubs7 = [[JEF United Chiba]] | caps7 = 8 | goals7 = 0\n| pcupdate             = 23:06, 21 April 2019 (UTC)\n}}\n'''Alan Lopes Pinheiro''' (\u30a2\u30e9\u30f3\u30fb\u30d4\u30cb\u30a7\u30a4\u30ed, born 13 May 1992) is a [[Brazil]]ian [[association football|footballer]]. He plays as a [[Forward (association football)|forward]].<ref name=\"jleague\">{{cite web|url=http://www.jleague.jp/club/tokyov/player/detail/1300923/|publisher=jleague.jp|title=\u30a2\u30e9\u30f3 \u30d4\u30cb\u30a7\u30a4\u30ed\uff1a\u6771\u4eac\u30f4\u30a7\u30eb\u30c7\u30a3\uff1a\uff2a\u30ea\u30fc\u30b0.jp|accessdate=2016-09-22}}</ref>\n\n==Club statistics==\n''Updated to 23 February 2018''.<ref>Nippon Sports Kikaku Publishing inc./\u65e5\u672c\u30b9\u30dd\u30fc\u30c4\u4f01\u753b\u51fa\u7