a]]\n*[[Campeonato Baiano]] (1): 2013\n*[[Campeonato Baiano]] Runners-Up (1): 2012\n;[[Copa do Brasil Sub-20]] (1)\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n*{{Soccerway|alan-lopes-pinheiro/226586}}\n*{{J.League player}}\n*[https://web.archive.org/web/20170305013044/http://www.verdy.co.jp/itemview/template116_1_2518.html Profile at Tokyo Verdy]\n\n{{JEF United Chiba squad}}\n\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Pinheiro, Alan}}\n[[Category:1992 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Brazilian footballers]]\n[[Category:Brazilian expatriate footballers]]\n[[Category:Esporte Clube Vit\u00f3ria players]]\n[[Category:Cear\u00e1 Sporting Club players]]\n[[Category:Kawasaki Frontale players]]\n[[Category:Tokyo Verdy players]]\n[[Category:JEF United Chiba players]]\n[[Category:J1 League players]]\n[[Category:J2 League players]]\n[[Category:Expatriate footballers in Japan]]\n[[Category:People from Brumado]]\n[[Category:Association football forwards]]\n\n\n{{Japan-footy-forward-1990s-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{short description|Brazilian footballer}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=March 2020}}\n{{Infobox football biography\n| name           = Alan Pinheiro\n| fullname       = Alan Lopes Pinheiro\n| image                =\n| height               = {{height|m=1.80|precision=0}}\n| birth_date           = {{birth date and age|df=y|1992|5|13}}\n| birth_place          = [[Brumado]], [[Brazil]]\n| currentclub          = [[JEF United Chiba]]\n| clubnumber           = 21\n| position             = [[Forward (association football)|Forward]]\n| years1   = 2012\u20132015 | clubs1 = [[Esporte Clube Vit\u00f3ria|Vit\u00f3ria]] | caps1   = 21 | goals1   = 19\n| years2   = 2013      | clubs2 = \u2192 [[Cear\u00e1 Sporting Club|Cear\u00e1]] (loan) | caps2   = 1 | goals2   =1\n| years3   = 2013      | clubs3 = \u2192 [[Kawasaki Frontale]] (loan) | caps3   = 10 | goals3   = 0\n| years4   = 2014      | clubs4 = \u2192 [[Agremia\u00e7\u00e3o Sportiva Arapiraquense|ASA]] (loan) | ca