\u624b\u540d\u9451\"], 10 February 2016, Japan, {{ISBN|978-4905411338}} (p. 189 out of 289)</ref>\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|-\n! colspan=3 | Club performance\n! colspan=2 | League\n! colspan=2 | Cup\n! colspan=2 | League Cup\n! colspan=2 | Total\n|-\n! Season\n! Club\n! League\n! Apps !! Goals\n! Apps !! Goals\n! Apps !! Goals\n! Apps !! Goals\n|-\n! colspan=3 |Japan\n! colspan=2 | League\n! colspan=2 | [[Emperor's Cup]]\n! colspan=2 | [[J. League Cup]]\n! colspan=2 | Total\n|-\n|[[2013 J. League Division 1|2013]]||[[Kawasaki Frontale]]||[[J1 League]]||10||0||2||2||2||0||14||2\n|-\n|[[2015 J2 League|2015]]||rowspan=\"3\"|[[Tokyo Verdy]]||rowspan=\"3\"|[[J2 League]]||31||3||2||1||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||33||4\n|-\n|[[2016 J2 League|2016]]||25||3||2||0||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||27||3\n|-\n|[[2017 J2 League|2017]]||39||17||0||0||colspan=\"2\"|\u2013||39||17\n|-\n!colspan=3|Total\n!115||23||6||3||2||0||123||26\n|}\n\n==Honours==\n;[[Esporte Clube Vit\u00f3ria]]\n*[[Campeonato Baiano]] (1): 2013\n*[[Campeonato Baiano]] Runners-Up (1): 2012\n;[[Copa do Brasil Sub-20]] (1)\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n*{{Soccerway|alan-lopes-pinheiro/226586}}\n*{{J.League player}}\n*[https://web.archive.org/web/20170305013044/http://www.verdy.co.jp/itemview/template116_1_2518.html Profile at Tokyo Verdy]\n\n{{JEF United Chiba squad}}\n\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Pinheiro, Alan}}\n[[Category:1992 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Brazilian footballers]]\n[[Category:Brazilian expatriate footballers]]\n[[Category:Esporte Clube Vit\u00f3ria players]]\n[[Category:Cear\u00e1 Sporting Club players]]\n[[Category:Kawasaki Frontale players]]\n[[Category:Tokyo Verdy players]]\n[[Category:JEF United Chiba players]]\n[[Category:J1 League players]]\n[[Category:J2 League players]]\n[[Category:Expatriate footballers in Japan]]\n[[Category:People from Brumado]]\n[[Category:Association football forwards]]\n\n\n{{Japan-footy-forwa